name: Superman
wikiSummary: Superman is a song by the rapper Eminem featuring Dina Rae, released in 2003 as a single in the U.S. only, peaking at #15 on the Billboard Hot 100. It was from his worldwide hit album, The Eminem Show, which was released in 2002.
